      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Igel</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Erinaceus_europaeus_(Linnaeus,_1758).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cb/Erinaceus_europaeus_%28Linnaeus%2C_1758%29.jpg/330px-Erinaceus_europaeus_%28Linnaeus%2C_1758%29.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"232\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cb/Erinaceus_europaeus_%28Linnaeus%2C_1758%29.jpg/500px-Erinaceus_europaeus_%28Linnaeus%2C_1758%29.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cb/Erinaceus_europaeus_%28Linnaeus%2C_1758%29.jpg/960px-Erinaceus_europaeus_%28Linnaeus%2C_1758%29.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Erinaceus_europaeus_(Linnaeus,_1758).jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>European hedgehog - an Igel <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Igel</b>,<br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> by <a href=\"/Volodymyr_Shcherbyna\" title=\"Volodymyr Shcherbyna\">Volodymyr Shcherbyna</a> licensed under the  <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GPL</a>, \ninitially based on <a href=\"/GreKo\" title=\"GreKo\">GreKo 2018.01</a> and following independent development since 2018. In August 2020, Igel switched to <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a> as a main evaluation function using <a href=\"/Dietrich_Kappe\" title=\"Dietrich Kappe\">Dietrich Kappe's</a> <i>Night Nurse</i> net <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> as default <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> participating in <a href=\"/TCEC_Season_19#Second\" title=\"TCEC Season 19\">TCEC Season 19, League 2</a>, and promoting to <a href=\"/TCEC_Season_19#First\" title=\"TCEC Season 19\">League 1</a>. In October 2020 Igel switched to own network trained on Igel 2.6.0 (Hand Crafted Evaluation) participating in TCEC Cup7 and in <a href=\"/TCEC_Season_20#First\" title=\"TCEC Season 20\">TCEC Season 20</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Features\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Features</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Board_Representation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Board Representation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Search\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Search</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Evaluation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Evaluation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Selected_Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Games</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2018\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2018</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#2020\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#2021\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2021</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#Misc_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-14\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Features\">Features</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Features\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Board_Representation\"><a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board Representation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Board Representation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Search\"><a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Search\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail Soft</a> <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a> with <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a> and <a href=\"/Reductions\" title=\"Reductions\">Reductions</a></li>\n<li> Variable <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a> with variable <a href=\"/Depth_Reduction_R\" title=\"Depth Reduction R\">R</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning#MoveCountBasedPruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Late Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search#StandPat\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Eval Pruning</a> (a.k.a. static null move) </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a> in <a href=\"/Node_Types#PV\" title=\"Node Types\">PV-Nodes</a> </li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Evaluation\"><a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Evaluation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a> (as of Igel 2.7.0)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mobility\" title=\"Mobility\">Mobility</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">Pawn Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Passed Pawn\">Passed Pawns Eval</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Square_Control\" title=\"Square Control\">Strong Squares</a> (B, N) </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Games\">Selected Games</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Games\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Igel 2.6-dev-3 x64</a> vs. <a href=\"/Booot\" title=\"Booot\">Booot 6.4 x64</a>, July 2020 by <a href=\"/TCEC\" title=\"TCEC\">TCEC</a>\n</p>\n<pre>\n[Site \"https://tcec-chess.com\"]\n[Date \"2020.07.17\"]\n[Round \"1.4\"]\n[White \"Booot 6.4\"]\n[Black \"Igel 2.6-dev-3\"]\n[Result \"0-1\"]\n[BlackElo \"3280\"]\n[ECO \"C01\"]\n[GameDuration \"01:08:12\"]\n[GameEndTime \"2020-07-17T20:16:56.946 UTC\"]\n[GameStartTime \"2020-07-17T19:08:44.259 UTC\"]\n[Opening \"French\"]\n[PlyCount \"118\"]\n[Termination \"adjudication\"]\n[TerminationDetails \"SyzygyTB\"]\n[TimeControl \"1800+5\"]\n[Variation \"exchange variation\"]\n[WhiteElo \"3424\"]\n\n1. e4 e6 2. d4 d5 3. exd5 { C01 French Defense: Exchange Variation } exd5 4. Bd3 Nf6 5. Nf3 Bd6 6. O-O O-O 7. Re1 Bg4 8. h3 Bh5 9. Be3 c6 10. Nbd2 Re8 11. c3 Nbd7 12. Qc2 Bg6 13. Bxg6 hxg6 14. c4 Nf8 15. c5 Bc7 16. Rac1 Qd7 17. Qb3 Re7 18. Re2 Rae8 19. Rce1 Qf5 20. Nh4 Qh5 21. Nhf3 N8h7 22. Nf1 Ne4 23. Bc1 g5 24. Qa3 f5 25. Ne5 Bxe5 26. dxe5 g4 27. Ng3 Nxg3 28. Qxg3 Nf8 29. hxg4 fxg4 30. Qh2 Qg6 31. Qg3 Ne6 32. Be3 Qh5 33. f3 gxf3 34. gxf3 Rf7 35. f4 Qf5 36. Rg2 Nxf4 37. Bxf4 Qxf4 38. e6 Qd4+ 39. Qe3 Qxe3+ 40. Rxe3 Rf4 41. Rd2 Re7 42. b3 Rf6 43. Rde2 g6 44. Re1 Rf5 45. Kg2 Kg7 46. R3e2 a5 47. Kg3 Kf6 48. Re3 d4 49. Re4 Rg5+ 50. Kf3 Rxc5 51. Rxd4 Rxe6 52. Red1 Ree5 53. Rd7 Rc3+ 54. Kf2 Rc2+ 55. R1d2 Rxd2+ 56. Rxd2 a4 57. bxa4 Re4 58. Rb2 Rxa4 59. Rxb7 Rxa2+ { Black wins. } 0-1\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2018\">2018</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2018\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?t=67890\">Introducing Igel chess engine</a> by <a href=\"/Volodymyr_Shcherbyna\" title=\"Volodymyr Shcherbyna\">Volodymyr Shcherbyna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 03, 2018</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020\">2020</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: 2020\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67890&amp;start=15\">Re: Introducing Igel chess engine - Igel 2.5.0</a> by <a href=\"/Volodymyr_Shcherbyna\" title=\"Volodymyr Shcherbyna\">Volodymyr Shcherbyna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 15, 2020</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67890&amp;start=16\">Re: Introducing Igel chess engine - Igel 2.6.0</a> by <a href=\"/Volodymyr_Shcherbyna\" title=\"Volodymyr Shcherbyna\">Volodymyr Shcherbyna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 01, 2020</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67890&amp;start=17\">Re: Introducing Igel chess engine - Igel and NNUE</a> by <a href=\"/Volodymyr_Shcherbyna\" title=\"Volodymyr Shcherbyna\">Volodymyr Shcherbyna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2020</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67890&amp;start=83\">Igel Generation Networks (IGN)</a> by <a href=\"/Volodymyr_Shcherbyna\" title=\"Volodymyr Shcherbyna\">Volodymyr Shcherbyna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 30, 2020</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67890&amp;start=91\">Re: Introducing Igel chess engine - Igel 2.9.0</a> by <a href=\"/Volodymyr_Shcherbyna\" title=\"Volodymyr Shcherbyna\">Volodymyr Shcherbyna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 25, 2020 </dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=74837\">Night Nurse 0.2</a> by <a href=\"/Dietrich_Kappe\" title=\"Dietrich Kappe\">Dietrich Kappe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2020</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2021\">2021</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: 2021\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76209&amp;start=195\">Re: New engine releases &amp; news 2021</a> (Igel 3.0.0) by <a href=\"/Volodymyr_Shcherbyna\" title=\"Volodymyr Shcherbyna\">Volodymyr Shcherbyna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 04, 2021 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76209&amp;start=292\">Igel 3.0.5</a> by <a href=\"/Volodymyr_Shcherbyna\" title=\"Volodymyr Shcherbyna\">Volodymyr Shcherbyna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 27, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=77503&amp;start=55\">Re: will Tcec allow Stockfish with a Leela net to play?</a> by <a href=\"/Connor_McMonigle\" title=\"Connor McMonigle\">Connor McMonigle</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 17, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=77503&amp;start=57\">Re: will Tcec allow Stockfish with a Leela net to play?</a> by <a href=\"/Connor_McMonigle\" title=\"Connor McMonigle\">Connor McMonigle</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 17, 2021</dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/vshcherbyna/igel\">Igel Home Page</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ccrl.chessdom.com/ccrl/4040/cgi/compare_engines.cgi?family=Igel&amp;print=Rating+list&amp;print=Results+table&amp;print=LOS+table&amp;print=Ponder+hit+table&amp;print=Eval+difference+table&amp;print=Comopp+gamenum+table&amp;print=Overlap+table&amp;print=Score+with+common+opponents\">CCRL 40/40 Igel</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ccrl.chessdom.com/ccrl/404/cgi/compare_engines.cgi?family=Igel&amp;print=Rating+list&amp;print=Results+table&amp;print=LOS+table&amp;print=Ponder+hit+table&amp;print=Eval+difference+table&amp;print=Comopp+gamenum+table&amp;print=Overlap+table&amp;print=Score+with+common+opponents\">CCRL 40/4 Igel</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc_2\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igel\">Igel from Wikipedia.de</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erinaceidae\">Erinaceidae from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hedgehog\">Hedgehog from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hedgehog_(chess)\">Hedgehog (chess) from Wikipedia</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Igel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/European_hedgehog\">European hedgehog</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?t=74619\">Night Nurse is Bad Gyal in disguise</a> by <a href=\"/Dietrich_Kappe\" title=\"Dietrich Kappe\">Dietrich Kappe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 30, 2020</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=74837\">Night Nurse 0.2</a> by <a href=\"/Dietrich_Kappe\" title=\"Dietrich Kappe\">Dietrich Kappe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2020</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67890&amp;start=17\">Re: Introducing Igel chess engine - Igel and NNUE</a> by <a href=\"/Volodymyr_Shcherbyna\" title=\"Volodymyr Shcherbyna\">Volodymyr Shcherbyna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2020</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301141124\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.069 seconds\